{"tid":2389761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英保釋案終審聆訊 律政司：被告涉國安法，法官不應考慮保釋條件","createTime":"2021-02-01T06:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T08:50:44.000Z","uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"be2f8deb14d89e5f1d12e9e60aa04b7085455989","tid":2389761,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"律政司一方又強調，「充足理由」的門檻較「實質理由」為高，並指法官於考慮國安法第42（2）條階段，不應考慮任何保釋條件。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方回應指，42（2）條並非「不得保釋」條文，而是「除非...否則不得保釋」（no bail unless)」條文，並指法庭於考慮相關條文時，應考慮被控人是否應被還押，而非是否應獲保釋<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/黎智英保釋案終審-律政司-涉國安法被告-法官不應考慮保釋條件/?fbclid=IwAR3xAWYA21E7ZJkVfLje1HCcPNxf9waL7yXXKSZttkmVDORZv_ZuoBafgJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8-%E6%B6%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xAWYA21E7ZJkVfLje1HCcPNxf9waL7yXXKSZttkmVDORZv_ZuoBafgJg&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1Gw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=75d604f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8-%E6%B6%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xAWYA21E7ZJkVfLje1HCcPNxf9waL7yXXKSZttkmVDORZv_ZuoBafgJg&h=1ebf6dcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/黎智英保釋案終審-律政司-涉國安法被告-法官不應考慮保釋條件/?fbclid=IwAR3xAWYA21E7ZJkVfLje1HCcPNxf9waL7yXXKSZttkmVDORZv_ZuoBafgJg</a>"},{"pid":"fe8161f81d7222232a2fbd4f5aa16efd186a4b86","tid":2389761,"uid":368881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img